snippet.title: Infinity Castle Dungeon - Official Launch Trailer #gametrailers
snippet.description:
INFINITY CASTLE DUNGEON: Indie 2D roguelike, which was developed for a year by a solo developer from Kyiv, Ukraine, is coming out on August 19, 2024 in Steam. Try to conquer the cursed castle and take out as many rewards as you can.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2621440/Infinity_Castle_Dungeon/
TikTok:@InfinityCastleDungeonhttps://www.tiktok.com/@infinitycastledungeon

E-mail: InfinityCastleDungeon@gmail.com

#trailer #gametrailer #indiegame #pcgame #steamgame #gametrailers
